item.dc:creator: @Sephiroth1 Sephiroth~
item.description:
@Sephiroth1 wrote:

trying to hack runescape? all i can say is: good luck

if you are playing a private server, then type ::pickup [itemID] [amount]

example: ::pickup 0995 5000

that will give you 5000 coins, if it doesn’t then you typed it wrong or the server doesn’t let you spawn items
